This project was created by George Papasotiriou for the ITC-4247-SECURE-SOFTWARE-DEVELOPMENT course in 2025. Its a local API Application with generic vulnerabilities along with a security testing tool (SecurityTester.java) (Fuzzer) to display those vulnerabilities. It was designed for Intelij IDEA. 
IMPORTANT BEFORE STARTING:
Download the latest releashe or the Final Project V3.rar to use the project in InteliJ IDEA.

OR 

Use Secure API App MyACGLibrary folder directly from github repo:
Step 1: https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/1208143224137318411/1449228683708731463/image.png?ex=693e22e3&is=693cd163&hm=d4b5831482c34a4094953185750dbcf12e182115c745d424ae1d870fdce495aa&=&format=webp&quality=lossless
